2
00:00:10,939 --> 00:00:12,439
<font color="#ffff00">DALAM DRAMA INI ADALAH FIKTIF</font>

3
00:00:40,944 --> 00:00:42,204
Saeroyi!

4
00:00:45,532 --> 00:00:47,834
Saeroyi!

5
00:01:04,301 --> 00:01:07,011
Ini 119, 'kan?
Ada orang tertabrak di sini.

6
00:01:07,012 --> 00:01:10,023
Tolong cek lokasiku
dan segera ke sini. Cepat!

7
00:01:10,849 --> 00:01:12,275
Saeroyi!

8
00:01:18,565 --> 00:01:19,482
<font color="#ffff00">PANGGILAN TERBARU</font>

9
00:01:19,483 --> 00:01:20,176
<font color="#ffff00">SEUNG-KWON</font>

10
00:01:29,785 --> 00:01:31,044
Hei, Geun-soo.

11
00:01:32,246 --> 00:01:34,589
Apa yang kau lakukan? Tangkap dia.

12
00:01:35,499 --> 00:01:36,842
Halo?

13
00:01:38,210 --> 00:01:40,795
Seung-kwon! Yi-seo diculik.

14
00:01:40,796 --> 00:01:43,557
Lalu Saeroyi terluka. Bisakah kau...

15
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,517
Menyebalkan.

16
00:01:49,429 --> 00:01:51,231
Geun-soo.

17
00:02:00,899 --> 00:02:02,576
Bawa dia.

18
00:02:35,642 --> 00:02:37,694
Rasanya aku pernah melihat ini.

19
00:02:46,570 --> 00:02:48,496
Mengertilah, Kawan.

20
00:02:51,241 --> 00:02:52,709
Ini tentang bisnis.

21
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,170
Coba cek dia.

22
00:02:55,245 --> 00:02:56,588
- Ya, Bos.
- Ya, Bos.

23
00:03:00,542 --> 00:03:02,844
Sial. Ayo pergi.

24
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:22,113
- Kondisi pasien?
- Umur 34 tahun.

25
00:03:22,314 --> 00:03:25,107
Korban kecelakaan. Tanda vital baik,
tapi tidak sadar.

26
00:03:25,108 --> 00:03:26,910
- Satu, dua, tiga!
- Satu, dua, tiga!

27
00:03:27,152 --> 00:03:28,453
Hati-hati!

28
00:03:29,696 --> 00:03:31,081
Ayo berangkat.

29
00:03:39,915 --> 00:03:41,749
- Mohon tunggu di luar.
- Ada apa ini?

30
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:43,834
- Kau tak boleh masuk.
- Lepas! Lepaskan aku.

31
00:03:43,835 --> 00:03:47,097
- Kau tak bisa masuk.
- Saeroyi!

32
00:03:51,301 --> 00:03:54,187
Pak, apa bisa mengatakan sesuatu?

33
00:03:54,846 --> 00:03:56,314
Pak?

34
00:04:04,856 --> 00:04:07,191
<i>Kemarin malam di dekat waduk
di daerah Pajin,</i>

35
00:04:07,192 --> 00:04:09,777
<i>Presdir IC, Park Saeroyi,</i>

36
00:04:09,778 --> 00:04:13,039
<i>menjadi korban tabrak lari
dan tak sadarkan diri.</i>

37
00:04:19,871 --> 00:04:21,372
<font color="#ffff00">DIREKTUR KANG, DARURAT!</font>

38
00:04:21,373 --> 00:04:22,440
<font color="#ffff00">PARK SAEROYI DIRAWAT</font>

39
00:04:25,669 --> 00:04:26,845
Ada apa?

40
00:04:31,174 --> 00:04:32,767
Detektif Oh.

41
00:04:33,844 --> 00:04:35,311
Apa ada masalah?

42
00:04:37,848 --> 00:04:40,755
<font color="#ffff00">EPISODE 15</font>

43
00:04:45,063 --> 00:04:46,448
Di mana Yi-seo?

44
00:04:46,898 --> 00:04:48,825
Dia tak bisa dihubungi.

45
00:04:49,901 --> 00:04:51,161
Entah dia di mana.

46
00:04:54,990 --> 00:04:57,834
- Ke mana kau pergi?
- Aku ada urusan sebentar.

47
00:04:59,578 --> 00:05:02,213
- Bisa bicara sebentar, Detektif Oh?
- Apa?

48
00:05:03,039 --> 00:05:04,507
- Aku?
- Ya.

49
00:05:16,178 --> 00:05:18,354
Apa? Diculik?

50
00:05:20,348 --> 00:05:22,525
Aku sudah cek kamera pengawas.

51
00:05:23,185 --> 00:05:25,728
- Sudah pasti dia diculik.
- Siapa yang berani...

52
00:05:25,729 --> 00:05:27,530
Mereka menculiknya dari RS ini.

53
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:30,950
Lalu ini ponsel Saeroyi.

54
00:05:31,651 --> 00:05:33,402
<font color="#ffff00">JANGAN HUBUNGI SIAPA PUN
DAN DATANG SENDIRI</font>

55
00:05:33,403 --> 00:05:35,121
Kalau begitu...

56
00:05:35,989 --> 00:05:37,832
kasus tabrak lari Saeroyi juga...

57
00:05:39,409 --> 00:05:40,710
Kita harus cari tahu.

58
00:05:41,536 --> 00:05:43,421
Aku harus pergi sebentar.

59
00:05:43,622 --> 00:05:45,715
Jadi, mohon jaga Saeroyi.

60
00:05:46,291 --> 00:05:49,168
Mau ke mana kau?
Kau harus lapor polisi dahulu.

61
00:05:49,169 --> 00:05:52,222
Kau lihat pesannya, 'kan?
"Datang sendiri."

62
00:05:55,091 --> 00:05:57,560
Mereka mengancam dengan membawa Yi-seo
dan Geun-soo.

63
00:05:57,719 --> 00:05:59,646
- Tak bisa libatkan polisi.
- Lalu?

64
00:05:59,846 --> 00:06:01,606
Apa yang akan kau lakukan seorang diri?

65
00:06:16,446 --> 00:06:18,122
Aku mau pastikan sesuatu.

66
00:06:18,406 --> 00:06:20,208
Sepertinya aku tahu pelakunya.

67
00:06:22,869 --> 00:06:24,295
<i>Tabrak lari?</i>

68
00:06:32,212 --> 00:06:34,639
- Park Saeroyi?
- Benar, Pak.

69
00:06:34,965 --> 00:06:37,308
Kemarin malam dia dirawat di rumah sakit

70
00:06:38,218 --> 00:06:40,019
dan sekarang masih belum sadar.

71
00:06:42,597 --> 00:06:43,982
Panggil Geun-soo.

72
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:47,110
Direktur Jang hari ini...

73
00:06:48,687 --> 00:06:50,363
tidak masuk kerja.

74
00:06:51,523 --> 00:06:53,825
Dia juga tak bisa dihubungi, Pak.

75
00:06:55,527 --> 00:06:56,828
Apa?

76
00:07:06,037 --> 00:07:08,080
"Kemarin malam di dekat waduk
di daerah Pajin,

77
00:07:08,081 --> 00:07:11,417
Presdir IC, Park Saeroyi,

78
00:07:11,418 --> 00:07:14,053
menjadi korban tabrak lari
dan tak sadarkan diri.

79
00:07:14,504 --> 00:07:17,006
Walau dia dengan cepat dibawa
ke rumah sakit,

80
00:07:17,007 --> 00:07:19,184
pada akhirnya Park Saeroyi..."

81
00:07:23,054 --> 00:07:24,731
Meninggal!

82
00:07:31,071 --> 00:07:34,165
Aku ingin sekali itu terjadi,
tapi sayangnya...

83
00:07:36,034 --> 00:07:37,961
dia hanya dalam kondisi kritis.

84
00:07:38,244 --> 00:07:39,587
Jang Geun-won.

85
00:07:41,498 --> 00:07:43,132
Aku kakakmu.

86
00:07:44,376 --> 00:07:46,219
Aku kakakmu, Berengsek.

87
00:07:50,757 --> 00:07:52,684
Kau sudah dapat keinginanmu, 'kan?

88
00:07:53,969 --> 00:07:56,396
- Lepaskan Yi-seo.
- Apa maksudmu?

89
00:07:59,307 --> 00:08:02,235
Apa kau tahu tugas terakhirku di Jangga?

90
00:08:03,603 --> 00:08:05,738
"Rekrut Jo Yi-seo masuk ke Jangga."

91
00:08:08,733 --> 00:08:11,494
Alasan aku masuk penjara
selama empat tahun...

92
00:08:12,696 --> 00:08:15,081
karena rekamanmu itu, 'kan?

93
00:08:18,368 --> 00:08:20,003
Bukan.

94
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:23,423
Kau hancur karena Ayah.

95
00:08:24,165 --> 00:08:26,551
Karena Ayah membuangmu.

96
00:08:31,339 --> 00:08:32,974
Dia lebih memilih Jangga...

97
00:08:33,675 --> 00:08:35,601
daripada anaknya.

98
00:08:36,636 --> 00:08:39,230
- Diam.
- Dasar sinting.

99
00:08:43,768 --> 00:08:45,862
Apa dengan begini Jangga jadi milikmu?

100
00:08:50,692 --> 00:08:54,203
Apakah aku sampai membuat onar
hanya karena Jangga? Aku tidak bodoh.

101
00:08:56,531 --> 00:08:57,915
Park Saeroyi.

102
00:09:01,369 --> 00:09:04,464
Park Saeroyi masih hidup.

103
00:09:21,014 --> 00:09:22,890
Anak kecil ini adalah kuncinya.

104
00:09:22,891 --> 00:09:24,275
Jang Geun-won!

105
00:09:28,271 --> 00:09:30,281
Kau dan Park Saeroyi.

106
00:09:31,524 --> 00:09:33,984
Melihat kalian datang karena dia diculik,

107
00:09:33,985 --> 00:09:35,828
ini jelas keputusan tepat.

108
00:09:36,654 --> 00:09:37,872
Bukan begitu?

109
00:09:43,661 --> 00:09:45,004
Apa katanya?

110
00:09:48,291 --> 00:09:50,927
"Aku sangat mencintai Park Saeroyi"?

111
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,978
Dia hampir mati untuk menyelamatkanmu.

112
00:10:01,721 --> 00:10:03,106
Bagaimana perasaanmu?

113
00:10:03,473 --> 00:10:04,941
Jang Geun-won.

114
00:10:06,726 --> 00:10:08,152
Dasar gila.

115
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:22,291
Melihat kau mengutukku,
aku merasa lebih baik.

116
00:10:32,293 --> 00:10:34,095
Kau tak bisa menutupi ini.

117
00:10:34,337 --> 00:10:36,264
Bagaimana kau menghadapi akibatnya?

118
00:10:45,056 --> 00:10:46,983
Kalau aku mencemaskan akibatnya,

119
00:10:47,725 --> 00:10:49,235
kalian sudah mati.

120
00:10:53,606 --> 00:10:55,199
Dasar sinting.

121
00:11:10,331 --> 00:11:11,841
Dasar gila.

122
00:11:22,886 --> 00:11:24,270
Apa kau...

123
00:11:25,930 --> 00:11:27,523
baik-baik saja?

124
00:11:27,599 --> 00:11:30,943
Tujuannya adalah menyiksaku.
Aku tinggal berpura-pura tersiksa.

125
00:11:31,728 --> 00:11:33,613
Dia mengikatmu dengan baik,

126
00:11:33,813 --> 00:11:36,574
tapi tidak denganku. Sudah jelas.

127
00:11:50,955 --> 00:11:53,257
Aku perlu kembali ke kantor.

128
00:11:54,334 --> 00:11:55,927
Kapan kau berikan sisanya?

129
00:11:56,711 --> 00:11:57,929
"Sisanya"?

130
00:11:58,922 --> 00:12:00,765
Pekerjaanmu masih belum selesai.

131
00:12:03,801 --> 00:12:05,353
Jangan berlebihan.

132
00:12:05,678 --> 00:12:09,690
Hubunganku dan Saeroyi kini buruk,
tapi aku kenal dia selama sepuluh tahun.

133
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:13,611
Aku sudah lakukan semua yang kau suruh.
Jangan macam-macam.

134
00:12:14,771 --> 00:12:16,113
Sepuluh tahun?

135
00:12:31,871 --> 00:12:33,172
Hei.

136
00:12:33,665 --> 00:12:35,299
Kenapa kau tertawa?

137
00:12:38,586 --> 00:12:41,055
Lalu kenapa kau menabraknya dengan van?

138
00:12:43,424 --> 00:12:47,645
Karena uang satu miliar lebih berharga
dari pertemanan sepuluh tahun kalian.

139
00:12:48,846 --> 00:12:51,023
Kalau begitu bekerjalah seperti anjing.

140
00:12:51,849 --> 00:12:54,151
Jangan bekerja setengah hati.

141
00:13:00,483 --> 00:13:02,493
Jaga mulutmu.

142
00:13:03,903 --> 00:13:06,497
Apa yang akan kau lakukan
bila aku tersinggung?

143
00:13:08,616 --> 00:13:11,544
Kau bisa lakukan apa pun
bila tak butuh uangku.

144
00:13:18,626 --> 00:13:20,052
Kau harus pergi, 'kan?

145
00:13:47,113 --> 00:13:50,458
Coba lihat. Masalahnya membesar.

146
00:13:50,783 --> 00:13:54,295
Jang Geun-won, orang gila itu,
dia gegabah.

147
00:13:54,912 --> 00:13:56,464
Aku khawatir, Pak.

148
00:13:56,664 --> 00:13:58,799
Bukankah lebih baik kita berhenti?

149
00:14:01,586 --> 00:14:03,095
Bos!

150
00:14:03,921 --> 00:14:06,015
Hee-hoon, kau di dalam?

151
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,142
Hee-hoon!

152
00:14:09,385 --> 00:14:11,470
Sudah lama kita tak bertemu.

153
00:14:11,471 --> 00:14:14,148
Hei, apa kabar?

154
00:14:14,557 --> 00:14:16,433
Apa Bos ada di dalam?

155
00:14:16,434 --> 00:14:18,861
Dia tidak ada di dalam.
Datang lain kali saja.

156
00:14:19,145 --> 00:14:20,488
Benarkah?

157
00:14:21,064 --> 00:14:24,700
Padahal aku ingin bertemu dengannya.
Haruskah aku tunggu dia di dalam?

158
00:14:24,901 --> 00:14:26,702
Maaf, Seung-kwon.

159
00:14:29,489 --> 00:14:31,707
Sudah kubilang, dia tak ada di dalam.

160
00:14:32,408 --> 00:14:34,951
- Apa?
- Kau pulang saja hari ini.

161
00:14:34,952 --> 00:14:37,004
Jangan buat situasi yang memalukan.

162
00:14:39,082 --> 00:14:41,175
Aku tak bisa apa-apa kalau begitu.

163
00:14:42,585 --> 00:14:44,053
Tapi kau.

164
00:14:46,339 --> 00:14:47,890
Kenapa bicaramu begitu?

165
00:15:12,198 --> 00:15:14,125
Untuk apa kau diam di situ?

166
00:15:52,071 --> 00:15:55,374
Sudah besar masih saja menggelikan
seperti ini.

167
00:15:56,826 --> 00:15:58,711
Kenapa tiba-tiba memeluk ayah?

168
00:16:12,758 --> 00:16:14,435
Aku merindukan Ayah.

169
00:16:17,972 --> 00:16:20,149
Kita bertemu pagi tadi.

170
00:16:21,267 --> 00:16:23,110
Apa ada masalah di sekolah?

171
00:16:29,066 --> 00:16:30,451
Masalah?

172
00:16:32,445 --> 00:16:35,289
Mungkin aku kelelahan.

173
00:16:46,667 --> 00:16:48,752
Bos ada di dalam, 'kan?
Aku Choi Seung-kwon.

174
00:16:48,753 --> 00:16:50,054
Hei!

175
00:16:50,796 --> 00:16:55,351
Buka pintu, Bos.
Kau harusnya temui adikmu ini!

176
00:16:55,885 --> 00:16:57,728
- Menyebalkan.
- Kemari.

177
00:16:58,638 --> 00:16:59,980
Kami bilang tak ada, 'kan?

178
00:17:00,473 --> 00:17:02,525
Beraninya kau mengacau
di depan kantor orang.

179
00:17:04,101 --> 00:17:07,354
Ada yang ingin aku tanyakan, Bos.
Bukalah pintunya!

180
00:17:07,355 --> 00:17:08,739
Dasar berengsek.

181
00:17:10,149 --> 00:17:12,284
Pergi saja.

182
00:17:18,741 --> 00:17:20,376
Kau baru saja menendangku?

183
00:17:20,993 --> 00:17:23,921
Situasinya sudah jauh berbeda dari dahulu.

184
00:17:26,624 --> 00:17:28,008
Benar.

185
00:17:28,626 --> 00:17:30,377
Aku juga sudah jauh berbeda.

186
00:17:30,378 --> 00:17:31,720
Lalu kau mau apa?

187
00:17:32,338 --> 00:17:35,266
- Kau ingin berkelahi denganku?
- Halo, kantor polisi.

188
00:17:36,133 --> 00:17:37,968
Aku di Gedung Minkang, Donggyo-dong.

189
00:17:37,969 --> 00:17:42,314
Aku dikeroyok oleh beberapa preman.
Aku takut sekali, cepat datang ke sini.

190
00:17:49,564 --> 00:17:52,199
Sakit. Pelan-pelan saja.

191
00:17:53,192 --> 00:17:55,402
- Astaga.
- Dasar sinting.

192
00:17:55,403 --> 00:17:58,873
Dia memang gila. Lalu apa maumu sekarang?

193
00:17:59,532 --> 00:18:01,000
Apa maksudmu?

194
00:18:02,493 --> 00:18:04,336
Polisi tentu akan datang.

195
00:18:04,996 --> 00:18:06,422
Kurasa...

196
00:18:10,376 --> 00:18:12,720
bajingan yang melukai Saeroyi ada di sini.

197
00:18:13,921 --> 00:18:17,266
Itu alasanku kemari,
tapi aku malah dipukul!

198
00:18:24,056 --> 00:18:26,901
Menurutmu apa yang terjadi
bila aku bilang itu ke polisi?

199
00:18:28,519 --> 00:18:30,237
Apa ada yang mau dengar

200
00:18:30,771 --> 00:18:32,406
omongan mantan narapidana?

201
00:18:33,649 --> 00:18:34,825
<i>Lalu?</i>

202
00:18:35,318 --> 00:18:36,785
Kau juga hancur?

203
00:18:38,321 --> 00:18:41,081
- Apa?
- Hanya bisa menilai diri sendiri rendah.

204
00:18:41,949 --> 00:18:43,500
Dasar pecundang!

205
00:18:47,413 --> 00:18:49,798
Kalian hanya bisa
menilai diri sendiri rendah.

206
00:18:50,416 --> 00:18:51,800
Dasar pecundang.

207
00:18:54,879 --> 00:18:57,139
Seperti katamu,
keadaan sudah jauh berbeda.

208
00:18:57,923 --> 00:18:59,516
Polisi tentu mau dengar aku,

209
00:19:02,553 --> 00:19:04,063
karena kini aku...

210
00:19:07,892 --> 00:19:09,492
<font color="#ffff00">CHOI SEUNG-KWON, DIREKTUR IC</font>

211
00:19:10,186 --> 00:19:13,155
...direktur Itaewon Class.

212
00:19:22,323 --> 00:19:24,750
Jangan berani-berani menilai hidupku.

213
00:19:30,706 --> 00:19:32,132
Bangunlah.

214
00:19:32,708 --> 00:19:34,051
Ya?

215
00:19:34,835 --> 00:19:37,012
Untuk apa tidur selama ini?

216
00:19:42,051 --> 00:19:43,985
Kau di mana sekarang?

217
00:19:43,986 --> 00:19:46,830
<i>- Aku di kantor polisi.</i>
- Apa? Ada masalah?

218
00:19:47,306 --> 00:19:49,391
<i>Apa Soo-ah ada di situ?</i>

219
00:19:49,392 --> 00:19:52,027
Ada, tapi dia sedang...

220
00:20:09,286 --> 00:20:11,171
Apa kau punya banyak teman?

221
00:20:14,291 --> 00:20:15,759
Ya, begitulah.

222
00:20:16,669 --> 00:20:19,847
Ayah tahu Soo-ah, 'kan?
Kami masih berteman.

223
00:20:20,548 --> 00:20:23,809
Aku bertemu pria bernama Ho-jin
dan kami sangat akrab.

224
00:20:24,427 --> 00:20:26,645
Aku juga dekat dengan yang lebih muda.

225
00:20:29,014 --> 00:20:31,608
Ada apa denganmu
sampai punya teman sebanyak itu?

226
00:20:33,769 --> 00:20:35,070
Entahlah.

227
00:20:37,106 --> 00:20:38,532
Siapa yang lebih muda?

228
00:20:40,484 --> 00:20:43,203
Seung-kwon dan Hyun-yi.

229
00:20:43,320 --> 00:20:45,822
Ada juga yang bernama Toni.

230
00:20:45,823 --> 00:20:47,166
Lalu ada...

231
00:21:06,594 --> 00:21:08,145
